{"tid":327214,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"陳妍希生完仔後唔同哂樣","createTime":"2017-07-18T14:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T18:17:08.000Z","uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9408e983eb294b32eb4efaf673f935a56ce3231e","tid":327214,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T14:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/224253_d04e0286269c40fcf58ae47919b7d2ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F224253_d04e0286269c40fcf58ae47919b7d2ec.jpg&h=fae1a446&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《那些年》的清純女神陳妍希生完仔仔後極速修身，樂於出席各種公開場合，她每次現身都會成為眾人的討論焦點，每次也會被討論產前產後的身材變化。日前，她上了台灣藝人小S的清談節目《姐姐好餓》進行拍攝，節目上小S也是一貫的刻薄言詞與陳妍希對話，她先問妍希是不是生完仔仔後可以橫着走路，妍希果真配合她的說話去扮蟹「打橫行」，場面非常爆笑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2tmzrg8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2tmzrg8&d=vzPM3nPDisIkFtDYl7qxzP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0d263d25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2tmzrg8</a>"},{"pid":"ebfbb52ca46a047fedd623cedc4d2f69aae2a525","tid":327214,"uid":63450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T14:48:58.000Z","msg":"我屌"},{"pid":"f966913e890b1cd5d1ae8192db34a39dd086d27c","tid":327214,"uid":63916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T14:49:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f4f3199d0643744f1b0813186d9d0935efdeb83","tid":327214,"uid":20914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T14:50:10.000Z","msg":"即係話佢未生已經等同生完咁肥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a749e8cf1fd0edbcde1e4bd978655afb64e0a081","tid":327214,"uid":40847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T14:50:49.000Z","msg":"睇錯陳冠希"},{"pid":"29e4dbcfb04a61af0d